data.description: Welcome to your new home in the prestigious Sossaman Estates Community! This property boasts 4 spacious bedrooms plus a den w/a closet cutout, perfect for all your needs. With 3 full baths, this home provides ample space for your family and guests. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by the warmth of real hardwood flooring & the grandeur of 10-foot ceilings. The heart of any home, the kitchen, features a large island w/a breakfast bar, granite slab counters, double ovens, a gas cook-top, & a pantry. The spacious owner's suite offers a separate exit to the covered patio, where you can unwind and enjoy the Arizona breeze. The outdoor space features an extended concrete pad, a built-in BBQ area & a large grassy area for play, New AC unit in 2019 & a 3 Car Garage w/Service Door & Cabinets.
